A place for me to store systems wide DotFiles for all my accounts.

mover info:
    moves all the files/ssh keys to their respective locations

weechat encrypted nickserv password:
    /secure passphrase <passphrase>
    /secure set freenode <nickserv password>  (maybe not this one)
    /set irc.server.freenode.command "/msg nickserv identify $(sec.data.freenode)"

